Car Auction System
A web-based car auction platform that allows users to buy and sell cars through bidding. This system enables sellers to list their vehicles with images and details, while buyers can place bids in real-time. Built with a user-friendly interface, the system supports user authentication, bidding logic, auction deadlines, and admin control for managing listings and users.

